data.comment: The match has started at Covebo Stadion - De Koel.
Jurgen Ekkelenkamp scores to make it 0-1 at Covebo Stadion - De Koel.
In the minute 12, Great play from Lassina Franck Traore to set up the goal.
Goal! Ajax increase their lead to 0-2 through a well-placed header from Lassina Franck Traore.
Antony Santos instrumental with a fine assist.
In the minute 18, At Covebo Stadion - De Koel, Danny Post has been yellow-carded for the home team.
Lassina Franck Traore puts the ball in the net and the away team extend their lead. The score-line now reads 0-3.
That's a fine assist from Nicolas Tagliafico.
The first-half is over at Covebo Stadion - De Koel.
In the minute 45, Goal! Dusan Tadic extends Ajax's lead to 0-4.
Sean Klaiber with an assist there.
In the minute 46, The second-half has started.
The home team have replaced Zinedine Machach with Yahcuroo Roemer. This is the first substitution made today by Hans De Koning.
Hans De Koning is making the team's second substitution at Covebo Stadion - De Koel with Simon Janssen replacing Danny Post.
In the minute 47, The away team replace Dusan Tadic with Quincy Promes.
Lisandro Martinez is on a sub for Nicolas Tagliafico for Ajax.
Chris Kum (Venlo) is red-carded and dismissed.
In the minute 54, Great finish from Lassina Franck Traore to give Ajax a 0-5 lead.
Hans De Koning (Venlo) is making a third substitution, with Roy Gelmi replacing Torino Hunte.
Ajax take a comfortable 0-6 lead thanks to Antony Santos.
In the minute 55, Lassina Franck Traore instrumental with a fine assist.
Jurgen Ekkelenkamp heads in to give Ajax a 0-7 lead at Covebo Stadion - De Koel.
Great play from Ryan Gravenberch to set up the goal.
In the minute 59, Goal! Ajax extend their lead to 0-8 through Daley Blind.
Lassina Franck Traore instrumental with a fine assist.
Stan Van Dijck is replacing Evert Linthorst for the home team.
In the minute 65, Lassina Franck Traore scores with a header and the away team increase their lead to 0-9.
Antony Santos with an assist there.
Klaas-Jan Huntelaar is replacing Ryan Gravenberch for Ajax at Covebo Stadion - De Koel.
In the minute 70, Zakaria Labyad is replacing Antony Santos for Ajax at Covebo Stadion - De Koel.
Ajax make their fifth substitution with Edson Alvarez replacing Daley Blind.
Ajax have been awarded a penalty...
In the minute 74, It's now 0-10 to Ajax as Klaas-Jan Huntelaar scores from the spot.
Goal! Klaas-Jan Huntelaar extends Ajax's lead to 0-11.
That's a fine assist from Jurgen Ekkelenkamp.
In the minute 79, It's now 0-12 in Venlo as Lisandro Martinez scores for Ajax.
Zakaria Labyad with an assist there.
The home team replace Giorgos Giakoumakis with Wassim Essanoussi.
In the minute 87, Goal! Ajax extend their lead to 0-13 through Lassina Franck Traore.
That's a fine assist from Zakaria Labyad.
The second-half is over. The match ends 0-13.
